{
  "title": "Developer Platform",
  "uid": "developer-platform",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "tags": ["developer-platform", "fleet"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "instance_id",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": "Prometheus",
        "refresh": 2,
        "query": "label_values(developer_worker_info, instance_id)",
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" },
        "includeAll": true
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "📊 Key Statistics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "At-a-glance health of the autonomous developer fleet — read these first, then drill into the tables and graphs below.\n\n- **Active workers** — EC2 workers currently registered and running.\n- **Workers started / Completed / Failed runs (24h)** — SOW runs over the last day.\n- **Avg run duration (7d)** — mean wall-clock time a worker spends per SOW.\n- **Failure rate (24h)** — failed ÷ total runs. Green < 5%, yellow 5–20%, red > 20%."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active workers",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "count(developer_worker_info)", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Workers started (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "count(count_over_time(developer_worker_info[24h]))", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Completed runs (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(developer_run_finished_at_seconds > (time() - 86400)) or vector(0)",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Avg run duration (7d)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg(developer_run_duration_seconds and (developer_run_finished_at_seconds > (time() - 604800))) or vector(0)",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Failed runs (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }
        }
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(developer_run_duration_seconds{outcome=\"error\"} and (developer_run_finished_at_seconds > (time() - 86400))) or vector(0)",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Failure rate (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 20 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }
        }
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "((count(developer_run_duration_seconds{outcome=\"error\"} and (developer_run_finished_at_seconds > (time() - 86400))) or vector(0)) / (count(developer_run_duration_seconds and (developer_run_finished_at_seconds > (time() - 86400))) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🏃 Workers & Run History",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 111,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "These two tables are tightly coupled — read them together. A worker shown in **Running workers** now will move into **Run history** once it finishes.\n\n- **Running workers** — every worker active right now and the SOW it is building (`Start Time` = when it began, `Elapsed Duration` = how long it has been running).\n- **Run history (last 30)** — audit log of recent finished runs: `Start Time` → `End Time`, with the computed `Duration` (`End Time − Start Time`) and `Status`.\n\nAll timestamps are shown in your browser's local time."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Running workers",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "started_at" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "dateTimeAsLocal" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Elapsed Duration" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "ms" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "labelsToFields", "options": { "valueLabel": "value" } },
        {
          "id": "convertFieldType",
          "options": {
            "conversions": [
              {
                "targetField": "started_at",
                "destinationType": "time",
                "dateFormat": "X"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "mode": "binary",
            "alias": "Elapsed Duration",
            "replaceFields": false,
            "binary": { "left": "Time", "operator": "-", "right": "started_at" }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "Value": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "exported_instance_id": true,
              "exported_sow": true,
              "job": true
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "instance_id": 0,
              "sow": 1,
              "started_at": 2,
              "Elapsed Duration": 3
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "instance_id": "Instance ID",
              "sow": "SOW",
              "started_at": "Start Time"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "developer_worker_info", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Run history (last 30)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "started_at" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "dateTimeAsLocal" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ended_at" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "dateTimeAsLocal" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Value" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "Duration" },
              { "id": "unit", "value": "s" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "labelsToFields", "options": { "valueLabel": "value" } },
        {
          "id": "convertFieldType",
          "options": {
            "conversions": [
              {
                "targetField": "started_at",
                "destinationType": "number"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "mode": "binary",
            "alias": "ended_at",
            "replaceFields": false,
            "binary": { "left": "started_at", "operator": "+", "right": "Value" }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "convertFieldType",
          "options": {
            "conversions": [
              {
                "targetField": "started_at",
                "destinationType": "time",
                "dateFormat": "X"
              },
              {
                "targetField": "ended_at",
                "destinationType": "time",
                "dateFormat": "X"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "deployment": true,
              "instance": true,
              "job": true,
              "exported_instance_id": true,
              "exported_sow": true
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "sow": 0,
              "outcome": 1,
              "started_at": 2,
              "ended_at": 3,
              "Value": 4
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "sow": "SOW",
              "outcome": "Status",
              "started_at": "Start Time",
              "ended_at": "End Time"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {
            "fields": {},
            "sort": [ { "field": "started_at", "desc": true } ]
          }
        },
        { "id": "limit", "options": { "limitField": 30 } }
      ],
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "developer_run_duration_seconds", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 120,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🖥️ Worker Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 30 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 121,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 31 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Host-level resource usage for each worker (node_exporter), filtered by the `instance_id` variable at the top.\n\n- **Worker CPU %** / **memory used %** — saturation per worker. Sustained > 85% (red) means a worker is starved; runs may slow or OOM.\n- **Worker network (rx/tx)** — bytes/sec in and out, useful for spotting large clones, image pulls, or model traffic.\n\nCompare series across `instance_id` to find an outlier worker."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worker CPU %",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 34 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 70 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 85 }
            ]
          },
          "custom": { "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed" } }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 - avg by (instance_id) (rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job=\"developer_worker_node\",mode=\"idle\",instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"}[5m])) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance_id}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worker memory used %",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 34 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 70 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 85 }
            ]
          },
          "custom": { "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed" } }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes{job=\"developer_worker_node\",instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"} / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes{job=\"developer_worker_node\",instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance_id}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worker network (rx/tx)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 42 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "Bps" } },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum by (instance_id) (rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{job=\"developer_worker_node\",device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*\",instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "rx {{instance_id}}", "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "sum by (instance_id) (rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{job=\"developer_worker_node\",device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*\",instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "tx {{instance_id}}", "refId": "B" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 130,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🤖 Claude Code Metrics",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 50 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 131,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 51 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Development activity from the Claude Code process driving each worker.\n\n- **Claude tool calls / min** — tool-usage rate broken down by tool (Edit, Bash, Read, …). A proxy for how hard the agent is working and where it spends effort.\n- **Live Claude output** — raw Claude logs streamed across the fleet.\n\n> ⚠️ Logs from all workers are interleaved here and can't yet be filtered to a single SOW's stream — treat it as a fleet-wide tail, not a per-run transcript. Per-stream isolation is a known future improvement."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Claude tool calls / min",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 54 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (tool) (rate(developer_claude_tool_calls_total{instance_id=~\"$instance_id\"}[5m])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "{{tool}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Live Claude output",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 62 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "Loki" },
      "options": { "showTime": true, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true, "sortOrder": "Descending" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{instance_id=~\"$instance_id\", job=\"claude\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "Loki" }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
